+To repeat the post-decoration refresh checks:
+
+```vim
+" Standard fixture: scroll, edit the active pane, wait for debounce, report
+<C-d>
+A post render refresh text post render refresh text<Esc>
+:silent WrapReport
+
+" Conflict fixture: deterministic programmatic Result edit and explicit invalidation
+:lua local s=require("codediff.ui.lifecycle").get_session(vim.api.nvim_get_current_tabpage()); vim.api.nvim_buf_set_lines(s.result_bufnr,1,1,false,{string.rep("post render ",20)}); require("codediff.ui.auto_refresh").refresh_result_now(s.result_bufnr)
+:ConflictWrapReport quiet
+```
